payload.text:
Masalahnya ada pada logika rotasi di dalam komponen `AnthuriumLeaf`. Sebelumnya, saya menambahkan logika "counter-rotation" (rotasi berlawanan) agar daun tidak terlalu miring, tapi ternyata itu justru membuatnya terlihat tegak lurus semua seperti tiang.

Saya akan memperbaikinya dengan:
1.  **Menghapus Counter-Rotation yang Agresif**: Membiarkan daun mengikuti kemiringan batangnya agar terlihat menyebar (kipas/roset).
2.  **Melengkungkan Batang**: Mengubah garis batang dari lurus menjadi kurva (Bezier) yang melengkung keluar, seolah keberatan menahan daun.
3.  **Memperlebar Sudut Layout**: Mengatur sudut penyebaran di `PlantVisualizer` agar lebih lebar (dari -60 derajat ke +60 derajat).

Berikut perbaikannya:

### Spesifikasi Perubahan
1.  **`components/Savings.tsx`**:
    *   Update `AnthuriumLeaf`: Mengubah `path` batang agar melengkung. Mengubah `transform` pada daun agar mengikuti arah batang.
    *   Update `AnthuriumFlower`: Memastikan bunga tetap relatif tegak di tengah tapi memiliki batang yang natural.
    *   Update `PlantVisualizer`: Mengubah konfigurasi `layout` array untuk memberikan sudut (angle) yang lebih bervariasi dan lebar.

# Updated files:

## components/Savings.tsx

Update AnthuriumLeaf and Layout to spread leaves naturally (fan shape)

```tsx
import React, { useMemo } from 'react';
import type { AppState, SavingsGoal } from '../types';
import { PlusCircleIcon, BuildingLibraryIcon, ArrowUturnLeftIcon, SparklesIcon, HeartIcon, TrashIcon, ArrowDownTrayIcon, ShoppingBagIcon } from './Icons';

const formatCurrency = (amount: number) => {
    if (amount >= 100000000000) { // If > 11 digits (100 Billion)
        return amount.toExponential(2).replace('+', '');
    }
    return new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID', { style: 'currency', currency: 'IDR', minimumFractionDigits: 0 }).format(amount);
};

// --- ANTHURIUM ASSETS (High Quality Vector Components) ---

const AnthuriumLeaf = ({ scale = 1, rotation = 0, stemHeight = 60, delay = 0 }: { scale?: number, rotation?: number, stemHeight?: number, delay?: number }) => (
    <g transform={`rotate(${rotation})`} className="origin-bottom animate-spring-up" style={{ animationDelay: `${delay}ms` }}>
        {/* Stem: Curve slightly outward based on rotation direction */}
        {/* M0,0 is bottom center. The curve bends slightly opposite to rotation to mimic weight */}
        <path 
            d={`M0,0 Q${rotation > 0 ? 5 : -5},${-stemHeight/2} 0,${-stemHeight}`} 
            stroke="#2E7D32" 
            strokeWidth="2" 
            fill="none" 
            strokeLinecap="round"
        />

        {/* Leaf Blade attached to stem end */}
        {/* We reduce the counter-rotation to let the leaf point outwards naturally */}
        {/* rotate(${-rotation * 0.3}) keeps it pointing mostly with the stem, but slightly lifted */}
        <g transform={`translate(0, ${-stemHeight}) scale(${scale}) rotate(${-rotation * 0.3})`}>
             {/* Broad Heart Shape */}
             <path 
                d="M0,0 C-25,-15 -50,-40 -50,-70 C-50,-105 0,-115 0,-115 C0,-115 50,-105 50,-70 C50,-40 25,-15 0,0 Z" 
                fill="#2E7D32" stroke="#1B5E20" strokeWidth="1"
            />
            {/* Midrib Vein */}
            <path d="M0,0 Q0,-60 0,-105" stroke="#66BB6A" strokeWidth="1" opacity="0.6" fill="none" />
            {/* Side Veins - More natural curve */}
            <path d="M0,-30 Q-15,-40 -30,-55" stroke="#66BB6A" strokeWidth="0.5" opacity="0.5" fill="none" />
            <path d="M0,-30 Q15,-40 30,-55" stroke="#66BB6A" strokeWidth="0.5" opacity="0.5" fill="none" />
            <path d="M0,-60 Q-10,-70 -20,-85" stroke="#66BB6A" strokeWidth="0.5" opacity="0.5" fill="none" />
            <path d="M0,-60 Q10,-70 20,-85" stroke="#66BB6A" strokeWidth="0.5" opacity="0.5" fill="none" />
        </g>
    </g>
);

const AnthuriumFlower = ({ scale = 1, rotation = 0, stemHeight = 80, delay = 0 }: { scale?: number, rotation?: number, stemHeight?: number, delay?: number }) => (
    <g transform={`rotate(${rotation})`} className="origin-bottom animate-spring-up" style={{ animationDelay: `${delay}ms` }}>
        {/* Flower Stem (Lighter Green) - Sturdier */}
        <path d={`M0,0 L0,${-stemHeight}`} stroke="#43A047" strokeWidth="2" fill="none" />

        <g transform={`translate(0, ${-stemHeight}) scale(${scale})`}>
            {/* Spathe (Red Heart) - Wide and Glossy */}
            <path 
                d="M0,5 C-30,-5 -50,-35 -50,-65 C-50,-95 0,-105 0,-105 C0,-105 50,-95 50,-65 C50,-35 30,-5 0,5 Z" 
                fill="#D32F2F" stroke="#B71C1C" strokeWidth="1"
            />
            {/* Glossy Highlight on Spathe */}
            <path d="M-15,-25 Q-30,-50 -30,-80" stroke="white" strokeWidth="3" opacity="0.2" fill="none" strokeLinecap="round" />

            {/* Spadix (Yellow Spike) - Protruding from notch */}
            <path 
                d="M0,5 L5,-45 Q0,-50 -5,-45 L0,5" 
                fill="#FFC107" stroke="#FFA000" strokeWidth="0.5"
                transform="rotate(-5)"
            />
        </g>
    </g>
);

// --- PLANT VISUALIZER COMPONENT ---
const PlantVisualizer: React.FC<{
    progress: number; // 0 to 100
    isCompleted: boolean;
    seed: number; // Used to randomize curves slightly
    type: 'finite' | 'infinite';
    skinId?: string; 
}> = ({ progress, isCompleted, seed, type, skinId = 'default' }) => {
    // Normalize progress (clamp between 0 and 100)
    const growth = Math.min(100, Math.max(0, progress));
    const isAnthurium = skinId === 'anthurium';

    // Procedural constants based on seed
    const curveDir = seed % 2 === 0 ? 1 : -1; 
    const leafAngleVar = (seed % 20) - 10; 

    // Height of the plant (max 150 units) for default plant
    const plantHeight = (growth / 100) * 120;
    // Number of leaves for default plant
    const leafCount = Math.floor(growth / 15);

    const renderLeaves = () => {
        const elements = [];

        if (isAnthurium) {
            // --- ANTHURIUM LOGIC (Component Assembly) ---
            // Define the layout of a full grown plant
            // Angles are wider now to spread left/right
            const layout = [
                { type: 'leaf', angle: -65, stem: 45, scale: 0.6 },   // Far left bottom
                { type: 'leaf', angle: 60, stem: 50, scale: 0.65 },   // Far right bottom
                { type: 'leaf', angle: -40, stem: 65, scale: 0.8 },   // Mid left
                { type: 'leaf', angle: 35, stem: 60, scale: 0.75 },   // Mid right
                { type: 'leaf', angle: -15, stem: 80, scale: 0.9 },   // Top left
                { type: 'flower', angle: 0, stem: 95, scale: 1.1 },   // CENTER FLOWER
                { type: 'leaf', angle: 20, stem: 75, scale: 0.85 },   // Top right
                { type: 'flower', angle: -25, stem: 85, scale: 0.8 }, // Side flower (optional)
            ];

            // Determine how many items to show based on progress
            // 0-100 maps to 0 to layout.length
            const itemCount = Math.ceil((growth / 100) * layout.length);

            for(let i=0; i < itemCount; i++) {
                const item = layout[i];
                // Don't show the second flower (index 7) until very close to end (90%)
                if (i === 7 && growth < 90) continue;

                // Dynamic scale based on growth to animate growing up
                const currentScale = item.scale * (0.5 + (growth/200));

                if (item.type === 'leaf') {
                    elements.push(
                        <g key={`l-${i}`} transform="translate(100, 170)">
                            <AnthuriumLeaf rotation={item.angle} stemHeight={item.stem} scale={currentScale} delay={i*50} />
                        </g>
                    );
                } else {
                    // Flower
                    elements.push(
                        <g key={`f-${i}`} transform="translate(100, 170)">
                            <AnthuriumFlower rotation={item.angle} stemHeight={item.stem} scale={currentScale} delay={i*50} />
                        </g>
                    );
                }
            }

        } else {
            // --- DEFAULT PLANT LOGIC (Vine / Stalk) ---
            for (let i = 0; i < leafCount; i++) {
                const yPos = 150 - (i * (120 / 8)) - 20; 
                const side = i % 2 === 0 ? 1 : -1;
                const scale = 0.5 + (i * 0.05); 

                let leafPath = `M0,0 Q${15 * side},${-10} ${30 * side},${-5} Q${15 * side},${10} 0,0`;
                let leafFill = isCompleted ? "#27AE60" : "#2ECC71";
                let leafStroke = "#1E8449";
                let rotation = (-20 * side) + leafAngleVar;

                elements.push(
                    <path 
                        key={i}
                        d={leafPath}
                        fill={leafFill}
                        stroke={leafStroke}
                        strokeWidth="1"
                        transform={`translate(100, ${yPos}) rotate(${rotation}) scale(${scale})`}
                        className="animate-fade-in origin-bottom"
                        style={{ animationDelay: `${i * 100}ms` }}
                    />
                );
            }
        }
        return elements;
    };

    return (
        <div className={`relative w-full h-52 flex items-end justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-t-xl bg-gradient-to-t ${isAnthurium ? 'from-orange-50 to-white' : 'from-blue-50 to-white'}`}>
            {/* Background Sun/Aura if completed */}
            {isCompleted && (
                <div className={`absolute top-4 right-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full opacity-50 blur-xl animate-pulse ${isAnthurium ? 'bg-red-200' : 'bg-yellow-200'}`}></div>
            )}

            <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200" className="z-10" style={{overflow: 'visible'}}>
                {/* Pot */}
                <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="potGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#8B4513" />
                        <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#A0522D" />
                        <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#8B4513" />
                    </linearGradient>
                    {isAnthurium && (
                        <linearGradient id="potGradientAnthurium" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                            <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#F5DEB3" />
                            <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#FFE4B5" />
                            <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#F5DEB3" />
                        </linearGradient>
                    )}
                </defs>
                <path d="M70 170 L130 170 L120 200 L80 200 Z" fill={`url(#${isAnthurium ? 'potGradientAnthurium' : 'potGradient'})`} stroke={isAnthurium ? "#DEB887" : "#5D4037"} strokeWidth="2" />
                <rect x="65" y="165" width="70" height="10" rx="2" fill={isAnthurium ? "#FFE4C4" : "#A0522D"} stroke={isAnthurium ? "#DEB887" : "#5D4037"} />

                {/* Seedling Stage (always visible if > 0) */}
                {growth > 0 && (
                    <>
                        {/* Default Plant Stem (Only for default skin) */}
                        {!isAnthurium && (
                            <path 
                                d={`M100 170 Q${100 + (20 * curveDir)} ${170 - (plantHeight / 2)} 100 ${170 - plantHeight}`} 
                                stroke={isCompleted ? "#1E8449" : "#27AE60"} 
                                strokeWidth={Math.max(2, growth / 20)} 
                                fill="none" 
                                strokeLinecap="round"
                                className="transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"
                            />
                        )}

                        {/* Leaves / Flowers */}
                        {renderLeaves()}

                        {/* Default Flower Logic (Only for default plant) */}
                        {(isCompleted || (growth >= 90 && !isAnthurium)) && !isAnthurium && (
                            <g transform={`translate(100, ${170 - plantHeight})`} className="animate-bounce-slow">
                                <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="8" fill="#F1C40F" />
                                {[0, 45, 90, 135, 180, 225, 270, 315].map((deg, i) => (
                                    <ellipse 
                                        key={i}
                                        cx="0" 
                                        cy="-12" 
                                        rx="6" 
                                        ry="10" 
                                        fill={seed % 2 === 0 ? "#E74C3C" : "#9B59B6"} 
                                        transform={`rotate(${deg})`} 
                                    />
                                ))}
                            </g>
                        )}

                         {/* Bud (If approaching goal, for default plant) */}
                         {!isCompleted && !isAnthurium && growth > 70 && growth < 90 && (
                            <circle cx="100" cy={170 - plantHeight} r="6" fill="#2ECC71" stroke="#1E8449" />
                        )}
                    </>
                )}

                {/* Empty State / Soil */}
                {growth === 0 && (
                    <circle cx="100" cy="170" r="3" fill="#5D4037" />
                )}
            </svg>

            {/* Progress Badge Overlay */}
            <div className="absolute bottom-2 right-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm px-2 py-1 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold text-primary-navy shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                {Math.floor(growth)}%
            </div>
        </div>
    );
};

// --- HIGH FIDELITY PET VISUALIZER COMPONENT (SWAN) ---
const PetVisualizer: React.FC<{
    progress: number;
    isCompleted: boolean;
    seed: number;
    type: 'finite' | 'infinite';
    skinId?: string; 
}> = ({ progress, isCompleted, seed, skinId = 'default' }) => {
    // Determine Stage
    let stage: 'egg' | 'baby' | 'teen' | 'adult' | 'legendary' = 'egg';
    if (progress >= 100 || isCompleted) stage = 'legendary';
    else if (progress >= 80) stage = 'adult';
    else if (progress >= 50) stage = 'teen';
    else if (progress >= 20) stage = 'baby';

    const isSwan = skinId === 'swan';

    // Procedural Color Palettes based on seed (Only for default pet)
    const palettes = [
        { name: 'Phoenix', primary: '#FF4500', secondary: '#FFA500', accent: '#FFD700', dark: '#8B0000' }, 
        { name: 'Sapphire', primary: '#1E90FF', secondary: '#00BFFF', accent: '#E0FFFF', dark: '#00008B' }, 
        { name: 'Emerald', primary: '#228B22', secondary: '#32CD32', accent: '#98FB98', dark: '#006400' }, 
        { name: 'Amethyst', primary: '#9370DB', secondary: '#BA55D3', accent: '#E6E6FA', dark: '#4B0082' }, 
        { name: 'Gold', primary: '#DAA520', secondary: '#FFD700', accent: '#FFFACD', dark: '#8B4513' }, 
    ];

    const p = isSwan ? {} as any : palettes[seed % palettes.length];

    return (
        <div className={`relative w-full h-56 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-t-xl bg-gradient-to-t ${isSwan ? 'from-sky-100 to-white' : 'from-gray-100 to-white'} group`}>

            {/* Environment / Background Elements */}
            {isSwan ? (
                // Water effect for Swan
                <div className="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-20 overflow-hidden">
                     {/* Back Water */}
                     <div className="absolute bottom-2 left-0 w-[120%] h-12 bg-sky-200/40 rounded-[50%] blur-sm animate-[sway_4s_ease-in-out_infinite_alternate]"></div>
                     {/* Front Water */}
                     <div className="absolute -bottom-4 left-[-10%] w-[120%] h-16 bg-sky-300/30 rounded-[50%] blur-md animate-[sway_5s_ease-in-out_infinite_alternate-reverse]"></div>
                </div>
            ) : (
                <div className="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-12 bg-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[50%] blur-xl transform scale-x-150 translate-y-6 opacity-60"></div>
            )}

            {/* Interactive Elements on Hover */}
            <div className="absolute top-4 right-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500">
                <HeartIcon className="w-6 h-6 text-pink-400 animate-bounce" />
            </div>

            <svg width="220" height="200" viewBox="0 0 220 200" className="z-10 drop-shadow-lg" style={{overflow: 'visible'}}>
                <defs>
                    <linearGradient id={`gradBody-${seed}`} x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stopColor={p.secondary} />
                        <stop offset="100%" stopColor={p.primary} />
                    </linearGradient>
                    <linearGradient id={`gradWing-${seed}`} x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stopColor={p.accent} />
                        <stop offset="100%" stopColor={p.secondary} />
                    </linearGradient>

                    {/* SWAN SPECIFIC GRADIENTS */}
                    <linearGradient id="gradSwanBody" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#FFFFFF" />
                        <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#ECEFF1" />
                    </linearGradient>
                    <linearGradient id="gradSwanWing" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#FFFFFF" />
                        <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#CFD8DC" />
                    </linearGradient>
                    <linearGradient id="gradGoldEgg" x1="30%" y1="30%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#FFF59D" />
                        <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#FBC02D" />
                        <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#F57F17" />
                    </linearGradient>

                    <filter id="glow">
                        <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="2.5" result="coloredBlur"/>
                        <feMerge>
                            <feMergeNode in="coloredBlur"/>
                            <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
                        </feMerge>
                    </filter>
                </defs>

                {/* --- STAGE 1: REALISTIC EGG (0-20%) --- */}
                {stage === 'egg' && (
                    <g className="animate-[wiggle_3s_ease-in-out_infinite] origin-bottom">
                        <ellipse cx="110" cy="175" rx="35" ry="8" fill="black" opacity="0.2" />
                        <path 
                            d="M110,40 C140,40 160,100 160,140 C160,170 140,180 110,180 C80,180 60,170 60,140 C60,100 80,40 110,40 Z" 
                            fill={isSwan ? "url(#gradGoldEgg)" : `url(#gradBody-${seed})`} 
                            stroke={isSwan ? "#F57F17" : p.dark}
                            strokeWidth="1"
                        />
                        {/* Highlights */}
                        <ellipse cx="95" cy="80" rx="10" ry="25" fill="white" opacity="0.4" transform="rotate(-15 95 80)" />
                        {isSwan && <circle cx="110" cy="140" r="40" fill="url(#gradGoldEgg)" opacity="0.2" filter="url(#glow)" />}

                        {progress > 15 && (
                            <path d="M110,40 L105,60 L115,70 L100,90" fill="none" stroke={isSwan ? "#F57F17" : "black"} strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" className="animate-pulse" />
                        )}
                    </g>
                )}

                {/* --- STAGE 2: BABY (20-50%) --- */}
                {stage === 'baby' && (
                    <g className="animate-bounce-slow origin-bottom">
                        <ellipse cx="110" cy="170" rx="30" ry="6" fill="black" opacity="0.2" />

                        {/* Body */}
                        <circle cx="110" cy="130" r="40" fill={isSwan ? "#CFD8DC" : `url(#gradBody-${seed})`} /> {/* Grey for Swan baby */}
                        {isSwan && (
                            // Fluff effect for swan baby
                            <path d="M70,130 Q75,120 80,130 Q85,120 90,130" fill="none" stroke="#B0BEC5" strokeWidth="2" />
                        )}

                        {/* Wings */}
                        <path d="M70,130 Q60,120 75,115" fill="none" stroke={isSwan ? "#90A4AE" : p.dark} strokeWidth="3" strokeLinecap="round" className="animate-[flap_0.5s_ease-in-out_infinite]" />
                        <path d="M150,130 Q160,120 145,115" fill="none" stroke={isSwan ? "#90A4AE" : p.dark} strokeWidth="3" strokeLinecap="round" className="animate-[flap_0.5s_ease-in-out_infinite_reverse]" />

                        {/* Face */}
                        <circle cx="95" cy="120" r="6" fill="black" />
                        <circle cx="125" cy="120" r="6" fill="black" />
                        <circle cx="93" cy="118" r="2.5" fill="white" />
                        <circle cx="123" cy="118" r="2.5" fill="white" />

                        {/* Beak */}
                        <path d="M105,135 L115,135 L110,145 Z" fill={isSwan ? "#37474F" : "#FFA500"} stroke={isSwan ? "none" : "#CC8400"} />

                        {/* Feet */}
                        <path d="M100,165 L100,175 M120,165 L120,175" stroke={isSwan ? "#37474F" : p.dark} strokeWidth="3" strokeLinecap="round" />
                    </g>
                )}

                {/* --- STAGE 3: TEEN (50-80%) --- */}
                {stage === 'teen' && (
                    <g transform="translate(10, 10)">
                        <ellipse cx="100" cy="160" rx="30" ry="6" fill="black" opacity="0.2" />
                        {isSwan ? (
                            // Swan Teen (Mix of white and grey, neck growing)
                            <g>
                                {/* Body */}
                                <ellipse cx="100" cy="130" rx="45" ry="30" fill="#ECEFF1" />
                                {/* Wing */}
                                <path d="M60,120 Q100,110 120,130 Q100,150 60,140" fill="#CFD8DC" />
                                {/* Neck beginning to curve */}
                                <path d="M130,120 Q150,100 130,70 Q120,60 100,60" fill="none" stroke="#ECEFF1" strokeWidth="18" strokeLinecap="round" />
                                {/* Head */}
                                <circle cx="100" cy="60" r="14" fill="#ECEFF1" />
                                <path d="M88,60 L70,65 L88,70 Z" fill="#546E7A" /> {/* Dark grey beak */}
                                <circle cx="95" cy="58" r="2" fill="black" />
                            </g>
                        ) : (
                            // Default Teen
                            <g>
                                <path d="M60,120 Q60,90 100,90 Q140,90 140,130 Q140,160 100,160 Q60,160 60,120" fill={`url(#gradBody-${seed})`} />
                                <circle cx="100" cy="80" r="25" fill={`url(#gradBody-${seed})`} />
                                <path d="M100,55 Q90,40 105,35 Q110,45 100,55" fill={p.dark} />
                                <path d="M80,120 Q80,160 120,140 Q130,120 80,120" fill={p.secondary} stroke={p.dark} strokeWidth="1" />
                                <circle cx="90" cy="75" r="4" fill="black" />
                                <path d="M75,80 L60,85 L75,90 Z" fill="#FFA500" />
                            </g>
                        )}
                    </g>
                )}

                {/* --- STAGE 4: ADULT (80-100%) --- */}
                {(stage === 'adult' || stage === 'legendary') && (
                    <g transform="translate(10, 10)">
                        {stage === 'legendary' && (
                            <circle cx="110" cy="90" r="80" fill={isSwan ? "#E0F7FA" : `url(#gradBody-${seed})`} opacity="0.3" filter="url(#glow)" className="animate-pulse" />
                        )}

                        {isSwan ? (
                            // SWAN ADULT (High Fidelity Anatomy)
                            <g className="animate-[float_4s_ease-in-out_infinite]">
                                {/* Tail Feathers */}
                                <path d="M30,130 Q20,110 40,120 Q20,130 40,135 Q25,145 45,145" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="#ECEFF1" strokeWidth="1"/>

                                {/* Main Body Shape */}
                                <path 
                                    d="M40,145 C40,170 140,170 150,140 C155,120 120,110 100,120" 
                                    fill="url(#gradSwanBody)" 
                                />

                                {/* Detailed Wing */}
                                <path 
                                    d="M50,130 C60,110 120,110 130,130 C135,140 120,155 100,155 C70,155 60,140 50,130" 
                                    fill="url(#gradSwanWing)" 
                                    stroke="#CFD8DC"
                                    strokeWidth="0.5"
                                />
                                {/* Wing Feathers detail */}
                                <path d="M60,130 Q90,120 120,130" fill="none" stroke="#ECEFF1" strokeWidth="1"/>
                                <path d="M65,135 Q90,128 115,135" fill="none" stroke="#ECEFF1" strokeWidth="1"/>

                                {/* Neck & Head (One smooth path for better anatomy) */}
                                <path 
                                    d="M135,140 
                                       C170,110 175,90 160,75
                                       C150,65 145,65 150,50
                                       C153,42 165,40 172,45
                                       C175,48 175,52 170,52
                                       C160,52 155,45 160,42
                                       L172,45 
                                       C180,35 150,30 145,50
                                       C140,70 160,100 130,135"
                                    fill="#FFFFFF"
                                />

                                {/* Face Details */}
                                <g transform="translate(172, 45)">
                                    {/* Black Knob (The "Mask" of Mute Swan) */}
                                    <path d="M0,0 C-3,-3 -2,-6 2,-2 C3,-1 2,2 0,0 Z" fill="black" />
                                    {/* Beak (Orange) */}
                                    <path d="M2,-1 L12,2 L2,5 Z" fill="#FF9800" />
                                    {/* Eye */}
                                    <circle cx="-2" cy="1" r="1.2" fill="black" />
                                </g>

                                {/* Reflection in water */}
